data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT & BONUS OF NEW ROOF BEING INSTALLED MID JANUARY 2024! Welcome to this lovely four-bedroom, two and half-bathroom home, perfectly located just two blocks from St. Cloud’s Lakefront Park and the vibrant heart of downtown St. Cloud.  Nestled on a corner lot, almost a quarter acre in size, it boasts a charming brick exterior and welcoming front porch. Extensively renovated in 2020, the house was completely overhauled including new drywall and flooring. The kitchen is complete with lots of natural sunlight, shaker-style cabinetry, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Adding to the charm, the renovation also included the replacement of windows and the sliding door in the Florida room, as well as a retextured ceiling across the entire house. The upgrades continued in 2023 with the full renovation of the fourth bedroom and powder room. This recent refresh included new floors, drywall, vanity, and hardware. Additionally, all windows and the front door were replaced, and the guest bathroom received a new shower/tub and hardware. The Florida room was revitalized with fresh paint, an epoxy floor, and a new exterior door. Step outside to discover a huge backyard, offering ample space for a potential pool installation, and perfect for outdoor gatherings. The home’s prime location means you're never far from adventure. Lake Nona, beautiful beaches, and world-renowned theme parks are all within easy driving distance. Imagine starting your days with lakeside walks, enjoying afternoons at Lakefront Beach, and savoring delicious meals at Crabby Bills before a riverboat excursion. Sounds like the life, right? Enjoy your life and schedule your private showing today.
